```powershell
cd erp/server
npm run dev
```

### 2. Launching the Frontend Web Application
```powershell
cd erp/client
npm run dev
```

### 3. Running Automated Test Suites
```powershell
cd erp/server
npm test
```

### 4. Monitoring Production Logs
Logs are automatically categorized and rotated daily under `erp/server/logs/`:
- `combined-YYYY-MM-DD.log`: Full system activity.
- `error-YYYY-MM-DD.log`: Exception tracking.
- `http-YYYY-MM-DD.log`: Structured HTTP request logs.
- `audit-YYYY-MM-DD.log`: Financial transaction compliance audit trails.

